      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted. GCI = 1.8% for NIH between 6.4M and 14.7M cell meshes. Richardson-extrapolated value used as reference. Medium mesh (6.4M cells) adopted for production runs balancing accuracy and computational cost."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
