      "rationale": "Simulated NIH agrees with in-vitro measurements within 6.8% (maximum absolute deviation) across all 5 flow-speed combinations. Systematic bias of +2.1% attributed to blood analog viscosity model; within acceptable uncertainty budget."
    },
