      "rationale": "Validation used FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry identical to COU device. Operating points span clinical CPB flow range (3–6 L/min, 2500–4000 RPM). Porcine blood analog at 37°C matches COU fluid assumption. No extrapolation beyond validated envelope required."
